text: Carmela Toso (born 30 September 1912, date of death unknown) was an Italian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
